## Decision

### No Hardware MFA Key for Root Account

With team members responsible for root account credentials not being based at a single location, a hardware MFA is impractical for emergency use.

The team will instead maintain software MFA devices and require their presence.

## Consequences

The team will instead maintain software MFA devices and require their presence.
